527
00:55:55,719 --> 00:55:56,719
[SPEAKER_06] Kako tebi to izgleda?

528
00:55:56,719 --> 00:55:57,719
[SPEAKER_06] Evo, govorim, evo, snimamo, snimamo.

529
00:55:57,719 --> 00:55:58,719
